    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example maintains its mechanical integrity with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential providing exceptional traction. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system remains responsive throughout the power band. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, its suspension geometry and linear power delivery remain uncompromising. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist seeking the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated M-division era.",
